These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, august
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | onion   | orange   |
| Birthday   | august | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different games are played: billiard, monopoly
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Game   | monopoly | billiard   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, scooter
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, r&b
1. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Transport          | scooter | trike |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b     |

 #################################

 
